- Remove the broad guard I previously added in SimplifyIndVar.cpp that affected other tests.
- Add a precise fold in IndVarSimplify::rewriteFirstIterationLoopExitValues to detect the pattern zext(add %phi, %phi) where %phi is the header PHI and compute the constant from the preheader incoming value, preserving i16 wrap.
Then I will rebuild the relevant libraries and submit the patch for verification.

```bash
